\nresults of the linear deterministic model follow, where capacity is replaced\nwith approximate capacity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2011 20:36:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2013 17:52:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2013 08:19:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
