s between statistical precision and computational\nefficiency in high-dimensional estimation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2011 23:53:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2012 02:25:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2012 19:13:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-26"}
